title: EPIC DEFENSE OF DUNHARROW - Third Age Total War Gameplay
description:
Third Age Total War Gameplay - The Darklord's spies have spotted Rohan's camp at Dunharrow.  They march an army for a preempted strike against Rohan.  But Mordor's army does not go unnoticed.  The Silvan Elves mobilize a small force to aid Rohan in the enviable attack!  Enjoy the battle :D
